results.name: Avengers
results.description: Earth's Mightiest Heroes joined forces to take on threats that were too big for any one hero to tackle. With a roster that has included Captain America, Iron Man, Ant-Man, Hulk, Thor, Wasp and dozens more over the years, the Avengers have come to be regarded as Earth's No. 1 team.

results.name: Storm
results.description: Ororo Monroe is the descendant of an ancient line of African priestesses, all of whom have white hair, blue eyes, and the potential to wield magic.

results.name: Strong Guy
results.description: According to his own admission, Guido was a nerdy-looking kid in his early life, bullied by other children, but after he discovered his mutant ability at a young age, when he was struck by a school bus, no one bullied him again.

results.name: Wolverine
results.description: Born with super-human senses and the power to heal from almost any wound, Wolverine was captured by a secret Canadian organization and given an unbreakable skeleton and claws. Treated like an animal, it took years for him to control himself. Now, he's a premiere member of both the X-Men and the Avengers.
